parameters:
\nc<Saki>(I did it! With this, somehow... I've placed the real supply
box up there, so it should be fine.)
\nc<Broadcast>Now then, we will begin the hide-and-seek event!

\nc<Broadcast>If a succubus is caught, please make sure to tell the
customer to post a review! Otherwise, you won't receive your
reward.
\nc<Succubus>Really, how much more black can this get?

\nc<Succubus>Uh, they're not coming this way, right!? I need to escape
quickly...

\bustMsgExpression[1, 0]\nc<Saki>(They passed by! Phew, that was close. They wouldn't think
that someone is still here, right?)

\nc<Saki>(They really do it right away. But... I should be safe,
right?)
